## Windsurf AI Development Rules

### Stack: {{stack}}

- Go 1.23, standard project layout: cmd/ + internal/ + pkg/
- slog for structured logging — never global loggers
- Error wrapping: `fmt.Errorf("context: %w", err)`
- Table-driven tests with `testing` package
- No global state — constructor injection only
- Concurrency: `sync.WaitGroup` or `errgroup`, not `time.Sleep`
